ze 2.5 2.5) (bold yes)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "17ef5cc8-1ab5-4c75-8a07-0feaf26577d1")) (text "U5: ADXL345 Accelerometer | CS=GPIO5 | ±16g range, full resolution, 100Hz ODR\nU6: SX1262 LoRa Module | CS=GPIO7, BUSY=GPIO3, DIO1=GPIO10, RST=GPIO1\n    865.0 MHz India band | SF9, BW125kHz | 14dBm TX | U.FL antenna connector\n    NOTE: 50-ohm impedance-controlled trace required from module to U.FL\nJ3: e-ink Display FPC 8-pin | CS=GPIO19, DC=GPIO18, RST=GPIO17, BUSY=GPIO16\n    1.54\" 200x200 B/W | SSD1681 driver IC | zero-power image retention" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 10 87 0) (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "4cfbe6d2-8e46-41a6-9de7-c4d26f78c8c7")) (text "GPS MODULE (UART)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 10 118 0) (effects (font (size 2.5 2.5) (bold yes)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "700b073f-747a-4cc8-b21f-0b2a2f46ef00")) (text "U7: u-blox MAX-M10S | TX=GPIO21 (ESP RX), RX=GPIO20 (ESP TX) | 9600 baud\n    Separate 3.3V LDO (U12 AMS1117-3.3) for GPS power domain\n    LDO enable: GPIO controlled for switchable power-off\n    Backup battery pad: CR1220 coin cell for RTC retention\n    Passive antenna or active antenna with LNA bias" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 10 125 0) (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "83c704c4-04a6-49fe-8b76-6b1922608474")) (text "POWER SYSTEM" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 10 150 0) (effects (font (size 2.5 2.5) (bold yes)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "35a576cd-f8a0-432d-8173-48bfbd5c1740")) (text "J1: JST-PH 2-pin LiPo connector (1000mAh 3.7V)\nJ2: USB-C receptacle (TP4056 VBUS + ESP32 D+/D-)\nU8: TP4056 | USB-C VIN -> LiPo charge | 1A charge current | charge indicator LED\nU10: DW01A + FS8205 battery protection IC | overvoltage/overcurrent/reverse\nU11: AMS1117-3.3 | LiPo+ -> VBAT -> AMS1117 IN -> 3.3V -> all ICs\nD4: LED + R4(330ohm) battery indicator driven from GPIO15" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 10 157 0) (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "b6b83bd3-c518-46c5-a3b0-e5cf929613b7")) (text "INDICATORS, BUZZER & TAMPER" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 10 185 0) (effects (font (size 2.5 2.5) (bold yes)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "c153a123-fb11-41c5-ad8d-59bb51275ce7")) (text "RGB LED (common cathode): GPIO12->R1(330)->D1(RED)->GND | GPIO13->R2(330)->D2(GRN)->GND | GPIO14->R3(330)->D3(BLU)->GND\nBUZZER: GPIO11->R6(1k)->Q1(2N2222 NPN BASE) | Q1_COLLECTOR->BZ1->3.3V | Q1_EMITTER->GND\nTAMPER: GPIO0->R5(10k)->3.3V (pullup) | PCB trace: GPIO0->lid_pad->GND via conductive trace\n        Lid CLOSED: trace intact, GPIO0=LOW | Lid OPEN: trace broken, GPIO0=HIGH -> TAMPER EVENT" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 10 192 0) (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "53034897-dc8e-47ba-a412-d7dc1178d5eb")) (global_label "+3V3" (at 50.0 46.19 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "bdb58773-01a1-4f54-bbeb-5a171628214b")) (global_label "GND" (at 46.19 100.0 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "f25ce108-31ac-4aed-b947-699d1b0834a2")) (sheet_instances (path "/" (page "1"))))